sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant API Server
    participant GrpcCall Controller
    participant Unit

    User->>API Server: Create GrpcCall (targetUnit, type, action, ttlSecondsAfterFinished)
    API Server-->>User: Confirm creation

    GrpcCall Controller->>API Server: Watch GrpcCall
    API Server-->>GrpcCall Controller: Notify GrpcCall creation

    GrpcCall Controller->>API Server: Get target Unit
    API Server-->>GrpcCall Controller: Return Unit info

    alt TTL exceeded
        GrpcCall Controller->>API Server: Delete GrpcCall
    end

    alt StartTime not set
        GrpcCall Controller->>GrpcCall Controller: Set StartTime
    end

    GrpcCall Controller->>GrpcCall Controller: Gather Unit Agent endpoint
    Note over GrpcCall Controller: DNS: {unitName}.{unitset-headless-svc}.{namespace}.svc<br/>Port: container port named "unit-agent"

    GrpcCall Controller->>GrpcCall Controller: Create gRPC client
    GrpcCall Controller->>Unit Agent: Invoke action via gRPC
    Unit Agent-->>GrpcCall Controller: Return result/status

    GrpcCall Controller->>API Server: Update GrpcCall status (result, message, completionTime)

    GrpcCall Controller->>GrpcCall Controller: Requeue after 1 hour
